text: Tedi Supriadi (born 26 January 1996 in BandungPBDJARUM - Tedi Supriadi ) is a male Indonesian badminton player. He is a doubles specialist. He is from PB. Djarum, a badminton club in Kudus, Central Java and has joined the club since 2011. In 2014 he won the mixed doubles together with Mychelle Crhystine Bandaso at the Jaya Raya Indonesia Junior International Challenge. In the same year he reached rank 2 in the men's doubles section together with Seiko Wahyu Kusdianto at the USM International Series.
